Conclusions
This study provides additional data on the risk of acute myocardial infarction in patients receiving osteoporosis treatment. The results favour the cardiovascular safety of alendronate as a first-line choice for osteoporosis treatment.</p><p>KW  - Acute myocardial infarction</p><p>KW  - CPRD</p><p>KW  - Osteoporosis treatment</p><p>KW  - SIDIAP</p><p>U2  - 10.1007/s00198-021-06262-1</p><p>DO  - 10.1007/s00198-021-06262-1</p><p>M3  - Article (Academic Journal)</p><p>C2  - 35138412</p><p>SN  - 0937-941X</p><p>VL  - 33</p><p>SP  - 1579</p><p>EP  - 1589</p><p>JO  - Osteoporosis International</p><p>JF  - Osteoporosis International</p><p>IS  - 7</p><p>ER  - </p></div>
